The Fellow is the fitter for my service; though Valour in two Officers be too much for one Company, yet 'tis convenient there should be one such Officer; I for Conduct, he for Courage—I defie the whole Regiment to match us. He hopes for Pay; let him; I could never see any such thing, I believe it may be converted to other Uses. [Asi
